snippet.title: NARUTO TO BORUTO: SHINOBI STRIKER – Kawaki (Karma Progression) DLC Trailer
snippet.description:
Kawaki (Karma Progression) lands in Naruto to Boruto: Shinobi Striker! DLC 40 brings you Ninjutsu like Daikokuten: Shokatsu, and the Secret Technique of Karma Progression! Available May 24. #NTBSS
